name:                hooks-dir
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            run executables in a directory as hooks
description:         run all executables in a directory with the same 
                     arguments and environment and collect the results.
homepage:            https://github.com/ibotty/hooks-dir
license:             BSD3
